Gulnara Shahinian bụ onye nnọchi anya mba Armenia na onye edemede nke na-amụ banyere ịzụ ahịa mmadụ. Ọ bụ onye otu Group of Experts on Action Against Trafficking in Human Beings na onye bụbu United Nations Special Rapporteur on Contemporary Forms of Slavery site na 2006 ruo 2014.
Ọ gụrụ iwu mba ụwa na Saint Petersburg Institute of International Relations, nakwa English na Russian Linguistics na Yerevan State University.
